import React from "react";

function Login(){
    return <form className="form">
    <Input
    type="text"
    placeholder="Username"
     />
     <Input
    type="password"
    placeholder="Password"
     />
    <input type="password" placeholder="Password" />
    <button type="submit">Login</button>
  </form>
}
export default Login;
